{
  "title": "Get a permit to play loud music",
  "description": "Apply for a permit to play loud music at an event in Barbados. A permit is required before holding events with amplified music.",
  "categories": ["business-trade"],
  "service_type": "information",
  "stage": "alpha",
  "updated_at": "2026-05-28",
  "body": {
    "root": {
      "type": "root",
      "format": "",
      "indent": 0,
      "version": 1,
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "format": "",
          "indent": 0,
          "version": 1,
          "children": [
            {
              "mode": "normal",
              "text": "If you are organising an event, you may also need to apply for one or more of the following: ",
              "type": "text",
              "style": "",
              "detail": 0,
              "format": 0,
              "version": 1
            }
          ],
          "direction": null,
          "textStyle": "",
          "textFormat": 0
        },
        {
          "tag": "ul",
          "type": "list",
          "start": 1,
          "format": "",
          "indent": 0,
          "version": 1,
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "listitem",
              "value": 1,
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "version": 1,
              "children": [
                {
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "text": "a license to sell and serve alcohol. You must ",
                  "type": "text",
                  "style": "",
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "version": 1
                },
                {
                  "id": "6a183320bfdf3ba829d63233",
                  "type": "link",
                  "fields": {
                    "url": "https://liquorlicence.gov.bb/",
                    "newTab": false,
                    "linkType": "custom"
                  },
                  "format": "",
                  "indent": 0,
                  "version": 3,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "mode": "normal",
                      "text": "apply for a liquor license",
                      "type": "text",
                      "style": "",
                      "detail": 0,
                      "format": 0,
                      "version": 1
                    }
                  ],
                  "direction": null
                },
                {
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "text": " from the police.",
                  "type": "text",
                  "style": "",
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": null
            },
            {
              "type": "listitem",
              "value": 2,
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "version": 1,
              "children": [
                {
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "text": "a permit to play copyrighted music. You must ",
                  "type": "text",
                  "style": "",
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "version": 1
                },
                {
                  "id": "6a183320bfdf3ba829d63234",
                  "type": "link",
                  "fields": {
                    "url": "https://coscap.org/tariffs",
                    "newTab": false,
                    "linkType": "custom"
                  },
                  "format": "",
                  "indent": 0,
                  "version": 3,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "mode": "normal",
                      "text": "apply for a music license through COSCAP",
                      "type": "text",
                      "style": "",
                      "detail": 0,
                      "format": 0,
                      "version": 1
                    }
                  ],
                  "direction": null
                },
                {
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "text": ".",
                  "type": "text",
                  "style": "",
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": null
            },
            {
              "type": "listitem",
              "value": 3,
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "version": 1,
              "children": [
                {
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "text": "a health certificate to sell and serve food",
                  "type": "text",
                  "style": "",
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": null
            },
            {
              "type": "listitem",
              "value": 4,
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "version": 1,
              "children": [
                {
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "text": "permission to use the road. For example, if you are organising a moving party or carnival procession.",
                  "type": "text",
                  "style": "",
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": null
            },
            {
              "type": "listitem",
              "value": 5,
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "version": 1,
              "children": [
                {
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "text": "police presence – if you expect to have more than 1,000 attendees",
                  "type": "text",
                  "style": "",
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": null
            },
            {
              "type": "listitem",
              "value": 6,
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "version": 1,
              "children": [
                {
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "text": "fire service presence –  if you expect to have more than 1,500 attendees",
                  "type": "text",
                  "style": "",
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": null
            }
          ],
          "listType": "bullet",
          "direction": null
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "format": "",
          "indent": 0,
          "version": 1,
          "children": [
            {
              "mode": "normal",
              "text": "If there is an entry or ticket fee to your event, you may need to ",
              "type": "text",
              "style": "",
              "detail": 0,
              "format": 0,
              "version": 1
            },
            {
              "id": "6a183320bfdf3ba829d63235",
              "type": "link",
              "fields": {
                "url": "https://bra.gov.bb/",
                "newTab": false,
                "linkType": "custom"
              },
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "version": 3,
              "children": [
                {
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "text": "register with the Barbados Revenue Authority",
                  "type": "text",
                  "style": "",
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": null
            },
            {
              "mode": "normal",
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text",
              "style": "",
              "detail": 0,
              "format": 0,
              "version": 1
            }
          ],
          "direction": null,
          "textStyle": "",
          "textFormat": 0
        },
        {
          "type": "horizontalrule",
          "version": 1
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "type": "heading",
          "format": "",
          "indent": 0,
          "version": 1,
          "children": [
            {
              "mode": "normal",
              "text": "Who needs a license to play loud music?",
              "type": "text",
              "style": "",
              "detail": 0,
              "format": 0,
              "version": 1
            }
          ],
          "direction": null
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "format": "",
          "indent": 0,
          "version": 1,
          "children": [
            {
              "mode": "normal",
              "text": "Businesses, organisations and individuals need a permit if they want to play loud music. ",
              "type": "text",
              "style": "",
              "detail": 0,
              "format": 0,
              "version": 1
            }
          ],
          "direction": null,
          "textStyle": "",
          "textFormat": 0
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "format": "",
          "indent": 0,
          "version": 1,
          "children": [
            {
              "mode": "normal",
              "text": "Loud music means music you can hear outside the boundary of a property, or at a time when people would reasonably expect quiet.",
              "type": "text",
              "style": "",
              "detail": 0,
              "format": 0,
              "version": 1
            }
          ],
          "direction": null,
          "textStyle": "",
          "textFormat": 0
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "format": "",
          "indent": 0,
          "version": 1,
          "children": [
            {
              "mode": "normal",
              "text": "These groups need a permit regardless of:",
              "type": "text",
              "style": "",
              "detail": 0,
              "format": 0,
              "version": 1
            }
          ],
          "direction": null,
          "textStyle": "",
          "textFormat": 0
        },
        {
          "tag": "ul",
          "type": "list",
          "start": 1,
          "format": "",
          "indent": 0,
          "version": 1,
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "listitem",
              "value": 1,
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "version": 1,
              "children": [
                {
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "text": "whether they are selling tickets or their event is free",
                  "type": "text",
                  "style": "",
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": null
            },
            {
              "type": "listitem",
              "value": 2,
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "version": 1,
              "children": [
                {
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "text": "the start and end time of the event  ",
                  "type": "text",
                  "style": "",
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": null
            },
            {
              "type": "listitem",
              "value": 3,
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "version": 1,
              "children": [
                {
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "text": "whether they are hosting a single or a series of events",
                  "type": "text",
                  "style": "",
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": null
            },
            {
              "type": "listitem",
              "value": 4,
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "version": 1,
              "children": [
                {
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "text": "the number of attendees",
                  "type": "text",
                  "style": "",
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": null
            },
            {
              "type": "listitem",
              "value": 5,
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "version": 1,
              "children": [
                {
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "text": "whether the event will be held in a rural or residential area",
                  "type": "text",
                  "style": "",
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": null
            }
          ],
          "listType": "bullet",
          "direction": null
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "format": "",
          "indent": 0,
          "version": 1,
          "children": [
            {
              "mode": "normal",
              "text": "Venues can ",
              "type": "text",
              "style": "",
              "detail": 0,
              "format": 0,
              "version": 1
            },
            {
              "id": "6a183320bfdf3ba829d63236",
              "type": "link",
              "fields": {
                "url": "https://publicentertainment.bra.gov.bb/",
                "newTab": false,
                "linkType": "custom"
              },
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "version": 3,
              "children": [
                {
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "text": "apply for an annual permit to play loud music",
                  "type": "text",
                  "style": "",
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": null
            },
            {
              "mode": "normal",
              "text": " with the Barbados Revenue Authority.",
              "type": "text",
              "style": "",
              "detail": 0,
              "format": 0,
              "version": 1
            }
          ],
          "direction": null,
          "textStyle": "",
          "textFormat": 0
        },
        {
          "type": "horizontalrule",
          "version": 1
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "type": "heading",
          "format": "",
          "indent": 0,
          "version": 1,
          "children": [
            {
              "mode": "normal",
              "text": "Who is exempt from needing a permit",
              "type": "text",
              "style": "",
              "detail": 0,
              "format": 0,
              "version": 1
            }
          ],
          "direction": null
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "format": "",
          "indent": 0,
          "version": 1,
          "children": [
            {
              "mode": "normal",
              "text": "The following groups do not need a permit to play loud music:",
              "type": "text",
              "style": "",
              "detail": 0,
              "format": 0,
              "version": 1
            }
          ],
          "direction": null,
          "textStyle": "",
          "textFormat": 0
        },
        {
          "tag": "ul",
          "type": "list",
          "start": 1,
          "format": "",
          "indent": 0,
          "version": 1,
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "listitem",
              "value": 1,
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "version": 1,
              "children": [
                {
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "text": "educational institutions",
                  "type": "text",
                  "style": "",
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": null
            },
            {
              "type": "listitem",
              "value": 2,
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "version": 1,
              "children": [
                {
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "text": "religious groups",
                  "type": "text",
                  "style": "",
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": null
            }
          ],
          "listType": "bullet",
          "direction": null
        },
        {
          "type": "horizontalrule",
          "version": 1
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "type": "heading",
          "format": "",
          "indent": 0,
          "version": 1,
          "children": [
            {
              "mode": "normal",
              "text": "How to apply for a license ",
              "type": "text",
              "style": "",
              "detail": 0,
              "format": 0,
              "version": 1
            }
          ],
          "direction": null
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "format": "",
          "indent": 0,
          "version": 1,
          "children": [
            {
              "mode": "normal",
              "text": "The Commissioner of Police advises you should apply for a loud music license 4 weeks before your event. However, to be safe, it is a good idea to do it as soon as possible.",
              "type": "text",
              "style": "",
              "detail": 0,
              "format": 0,
              "version": 1
            }
          ],
          "direction": null,
          "textStyle": "",
          "textFormat": 0
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "format": "",
          "indent": 0,
          "version": 1,
          "children": [
            {
              "mode": "normal",
              "text": "The application steps are largely the same regardless of whether you are applying as an individual, or on behalf of a business, organisation or venue. ",
              "type": "text",
              "style": "",
              "detail": 0,
              "format": 0,
              "version": 1
            }
          ],
          "direction": null,
          "textStyle": "",
          "textFormat": 0
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "format": "",
          "indent": 0,
          "version": 1,
          "children": [
            {
              "mode": "normal",
              "text": "Write a letter or email to the Police Commissioner’s office at Barbados Police Service headquarters in Bridgetown. You must state:",
              "type": "text",
              "style": "",
              "detail": 0,
              "format": 0,
              "version": 1
            }
          ],
          "direction": null,
          "textStyle": "",
          "textFormat": 0
        },
        {
          "tag": "ul",
          "type": "list",
          "start": 1,
          "format": "",
          "indent": 0,
          "version": 1,
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "listitem",
              "value": 1,
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "version": 1,
              "children": [
                {
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "text": "your full name",
                  "type": "text",
                  "style": "",
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": null
            },
            {
              "type": "listitem",
              "value": 2,
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "version": 1,
              "children": [
                {
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "text": "your telephone number",
                  "type": "text",
                  "style": "",
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": null
            },
            {
              "type": "listitem",
              "value": 3,
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "version": 1,
              "children": [
                {
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "text": "your email address",
                  "type": "text",
                  "style": "",
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": null
            },
            {
              "type": "listitem",
              "value": 4,
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "version": 1,
              "children": [
                {
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "text": "your home address",
                  "type": "text",
                  "style": "",
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": null
            },
            {
              "type": "listitem",
              "value": 5,
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "version": 1,
              "children": [
                {
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "text": "the name of the event ",
                  "type": "text",
                  "style": "",
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": null
            },
            {
              "type": "listitem",
              "value": 6,
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "version": 1,
              "children": [
                {
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "text": "the event location ",
                  "type": "text",
                  "style": "",
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": null
            },
            {
              "type": "listitem",
              "value": 7,
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "version": 1,
              "children": [
                {
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "text": "the event date",
                  "type": "text",
                  "style": "",
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": null
            },
            {
              "type": "listitem",
              "value": 8,
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "version": 1,
              "children": [
                {
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "text": "the event start and finish times",
                  "type": "text",
                  "style": "",
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": null
            },
            {
              "type": "listitem",
              "value": 9,
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "version": 1,
              "children": [
                {
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "text": "a brief explanation of the type of event you are planning",
                  "type": "text",
                  "style": "",
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": null
            },
            {
              "type": "listitem",
              "value": 10,
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "version": 1,
              "children": [
                {
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "text": "an estimate of the number of people you expect to attend",
                  "type": "text",
                  "style": "",
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": null
            }
          ],
          "listType": "bullet",
          "direction": null
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "format": "",
          "indent": 0,
          "version": 1,
          "children": [
            {
              "mode": "normal",
              "text": "It may help your application if you include information on how you have considered the environment close to the event location. This might include the potential impact on neighbours, businesses, wildlife and infrastructure in terms of things like noise and traffic.",
              "type": "text",
              "style": "",
              "detail": 0,
              "format": 0,
              "version": 1
            }
          ],
          "direction": null,
          "textStyle": "",
          "textFormat": 0
        },
        {
          "type": "horizontalrule",
          "version": 1
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "type": "heading",
          "format": "",
          "indent": 0,
          "version": 1,
          "children": [
            {
              "mode": "normal",
              "text": "After you’ve applied",
              "type": "text",
              "style": "",
              "detail": 0,
              "format": 0,
              "version": 1
            }
          ],
          "direction": null
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "format": "",
          "indent": 0,
          "version": 1,
          "children": [
            {
              "mode": "normal",
              "text": "It can take up to 4 weeks for your application to be processed. ",
              "type": "text",
              "style": "",
              "detail": 0,
              "format": 0,
              "version": 1
            }
          ],
          "direction": null,
          "textStyle": "",
          "textFormat": 0
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "format": "",
          "indent": 0,
          "version": 1,
          "children": [
            {
              "mode": "normal",
              "text": "You will receive a decision from the police department in the area that your event is planned to take place. It is unlikely your application will be refused but if it is, the police will explain why so you can make changes to your proposal.",
              "type": "text",
              "style": "",
              "detail": 0,
              "format": 0,
              "version": 1
            }
          ],
          "direction": null,
          "textStyle": "",
          "textFormat": 0
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "format": "",
          "indent": 0,
          "version": 1,
          "children": [
            {
              "mode": "normal",
              "text": "If your application is approved, you will receive a paper and a digital certificate from the police department in the area where your event is planned to take place. Take your certificate to your event. It must be available for inspection if the police ask to see it.",
              "type": "text",
              "style": "",
              "detail": 0,
              "format": 0,
              "version": 1
            }
          ],
          "direction": null,
          "textStyle": "",
          "textFormat": 0
        }
      ],
      "direction": null
    }
  },
  "bodyText": "If you are organising an event, you may also need to apply for one or more of the following: \n\n- a license to sell and serve alcohol. You must [apply for a liquor license](https://liquorlicence.gov.bb/) from the police.\n- a permit to play copyrighted music. You must [apply for a music license through COSCAP](https://coscap.org/tariffs).\n- a health certificate to sell and serve food\n- permission to use the road. For example, if you are organising a moving party or carnival procession.\n- police presence – if you expect to have more than 1,000 attendees\n- fire service presence –  if you expect to have more than 1,500 attendees\n\nIf there is an entry or ticket fee to your event, you may need to [register with the Barbados Revenue Authority](https://bra.gov.bb/).\n\n---\n\n## Who needs a license to play loud music?\n\nBusinesses, organisations and individuals need a permit if they want to play loud music. \n\nLoud music means music you can hear outside the boundary of a property, or at a time when people would reasonably expect quiet.\n\nThese groups need a permit regardless of:\n\n- whether they are selling tickets or their event is free\n- the start and end time of the event  \n- whether they are hosting a single or a series of events\n- the number of attendees\n- whether the event will be held in a rural or residential area\n\nVenues can [apply for an annual permit to play loud music](https://publicentertainment.bra.gov.bb/) with the Barbados Revenue Authority.\n\n---\n\n## Who is exempt from needing a permit\n\nThe following groups do not need a permit to play loud music:\n\n- educational institutions\n- religious groups\n\n---\n\n## How to apply for a license \n\nThe Commissioner of Police advises you should apply for a loud music license 4 weeks before your event. However, to be safe, it is a good idea to do it as soon as possible.\n\nThe application steps are largely the same regardless of whether you are applying as an individual, or on behalf of a business, organisation or venue. \n\nWrite a letter or email to the Police Commissioner’s office at Barbados Police Service headquarters in Bridgetown. You must state:\n\n- your full name\n- your telephone number\n- your email address\n- your home address\n- the name of the event \n- the event location \n- the event date\n- the event start and finish times\n- a brief explanation of the type of event you are planning\n- an estimate of the number of people you expect to attend\n\nIt may help your application if you include information on how you have considered the environment close to the event location. This might include the potential impact on neighbours, businesses, wildlife and infrastructure in terms of things like noise and traffic.\n\n---\n\n## After you’ve applied\n\nIt can take up to 4 weeks for your application to be processed. \n\nYou will receive a decision from the police department in the area that your event is planned to take place. It is unlikely your application will be refused but if it is, the police will explain why so you can make changes to your proposal.\n\nIf your application is approved, you will receive a paper and a digital certificate from the police department in the area where your event is planned to take place. Take your certificate to your event. It must be available for inspection if the police ask to see it."
}
